---
title: Beyond Meat® Burgers with Roasted Wedges and Zesty Cilantro Mayo
description: The winning combo of Beyond Meat® and cilantro meet in this Mexican-inspired burger. Crispy potato wedges and a wholesome green salad make for satisfying sides.

